      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（先日、ミクのアドバイスのおかげで）\n（トリエルの作詞は順調に進むようになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Thanks to Miku's advice the other day‚)\n(The lyrics for TRINIYAiLE are progressing smoothly.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（お礼をしたいと伝えたところ、喫茶店に行ってみたい）\n（と言われ連れて来たが……気に入ってくれて良かった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I wanted to express my gratitude‚ so I suggested going to a café.)\n(And brought her here… I'm glad she likes it.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 25.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、大丈夫なの？\n今は、お客さんは誰もいないけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ is it okay?\nEven though there are no customers right now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "私がいたら、目立つんじゃないかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I'm here‚ won't I stand out?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ここは半個室で人目にふれないから大丈夫\n店長に話は通してるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a semi-private room‚ so you won't be seen by others.\nI've made arrangements with the manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（よく仕事の打ち合わせに使ってる店だけど……）\n（こういう気遣いが本当にありがたいんだよな）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We often use this place for work meetings…)\n(I'm really grateful for this consideration.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ミク。俺からもトリエルのことはいろいろ\n伝えたけど……実際に話してみてどうだった？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miku. Even I told you about TRINIYAiLE already‚\nbut how was it when you actually talked to them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、とても純粋で、優しくて……\n本当にいい子だなって思ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone is so pure and kind…\nI really thought they were nice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。俺が一旦席を離れた時は\nどんな話をしてたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. When I briefly left the seat‚\nWhat were you talking about?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.9000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
