      "text": "そしたら、「新幹線でいっぱい寝るから平気だよ」って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then she said‚ \"I sleep a lot on the Shinkansen‚ so it's fine.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
