      "text": "瑠依ちゃんは、グミのレタス味が好きって言ってて\n「それって美味しいの？」って聞いたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan said she likes lettuce-flavored gummies‚\nSo I asked‚ \"Are they delicious?\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.9000000001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.9
    },
    {
