      "text": "瑠依ちゃんが「美味しいわ」って自信満々に言って\n優ちゃんとすみれちゃんが困った顔で笑ってたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan confidently said‚ \"They're delicious‚\"\nAnd Yu-chan and Sumire-chan made puzzled faces and laughed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyokissa-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyokissa-00-noon",
