      "text": "レタス味のグミが好きなら、ネギ味のグミがあったら\n瑠依ちゃんは食べてくれるかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If there were gummies with onion flavor instead of lettuce‚\nDo you think Rui-chan would eat them?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mku_01_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　ネギ味……？　ど、どうだろうな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Onion flavor…? Hmm‚ I wonder.",
